/src/fuzz/artifacts/

# MkDocs documentation site build output
/site/

# Generated fresh on every Docs CI run by `export_openapi` (#1198) — never
# committed, so the rendered API reference can't drift from a stale snapshot.
/docs/api/openapi.json
.cache/

